#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmix; supports several platforms and sound drivers."
msgstr "&kmix; stöder flera olika plattformar och ljuddrivrutiner."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have both ALSA and Open Sound System drivers installed, &kmix; will "
"use the ALSA driver."
msgstr ""
"Om du både har installerat ALSA och Open Sound System drivrutiner, använder "
"&kmix; ALSA-drivrutinen."

